{
  "chapter": 85,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十五章（卷八第三章·反败为胜）讲述了寇仲与徐子陵在九江遭遇铁骑会伏击，被任少名、崔纪秀、常真、法难等人包围。两人以杨公宝库为饵，诱使任少名单挑。战斗中寇仲断刀、长枪皆毁，二人且战且退至预设钓丝处，借钓丝之力在空中发动反击。徐子陵以软鞭缠住任少名脖颈，配合指法点中天灵穴，寇仲补上一脚踢碎其胸骨，终将这名南方黑道霸主击杀。二人负伤逃至江边，恢复功力后前往与香玉山约定的会合点，途中在山丘上远眺美景，感慨海阔天空。寇仲豪言天下再无人敢小觑他们，徐子陵冷静提醒前路艰险。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ji_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "崔纪秀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下崔纪秀，见过徐兄寇兄。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "常真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位哥儿身手不凡，若肯归降会主，会主必不会薄待两位。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_shao_ming",
      "speaker_name": "任少名",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若要归顺，必须拿出诚意来。也不用我教你们怎么做吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "可否先让我两兄弟商量一下。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_shao_ming",
      "speaker_name": "任少名",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "随便！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "今趟不投降，必然没命。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "除非他亲手击败我们，否则怎能就这么不战而降呢？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_shao_ming",
      "text": "会主若想我们归降，先要击败我们两人，那我兄弟俩立即把'杨公宝库'的秘密如实奉上。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ji_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "崔纪秀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假若会主分别击败两位，是否又作数呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_cui_ji_xiu",
      "text": "我们两个小子乃后生小辈，兼之现在既伤且疲，若对会主单挑独斗，是否有些不尊敬他老人家呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fa_nan",
      "speaker_name": "法难",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就让贫僧来侍候两位小哥儿吧！何用劳烦会主呢？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_fa_nan",
      "text": "假若大师输了，可是等若会主也输了呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_shao_ming",
      "speaker_name": "任少名",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若不亲自出手，也难教你两人心服，来吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "终干掉任小子了，唉！他真厉害，恐怕风湿寒都杀不了他。但却……噢！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你也不知自己现在狼狈样子多么可笑，痛吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不笑就没有事，想不到在这种情况下，都给我们刺蛟成功。哈！哎哟！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "横竖要到洛阳去，不若顺道宰了宇文化骨，好为娘报仇。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "千万莫要得意忘形，今趟能杀死任少名，是有点幸运的成分。可能因他多行不义，终于恶贯满盈。而宇文化骨虽时运不佳，受挫失利，但怎都有宇文阀在背后撑腰，宇文伤更是与'天刀'宋缺齐名的宗师级武学巨匠，仲少你还是专心去争你的天下吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "但我怎可看着你一个人去冒险呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "一切都待找到'杨公宝库'再说吧！咦！有船驰来呢！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "看到吗？船上插着宋阀的旗帜，定是宋玉致来找我们。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们功力未复前，不宜与任何人碰头。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "寇仲来了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "由今天开始，天下再没有人敢小觑我两兄弟，谁要这么做，最后都须付出惨痛的代价。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这话仍是言之过早，我们是靠联手之力，又因预作布置，才能干掉任少名。应该说下次若再有人来对付我们时，就必是来者不善，善者不来，会教我们更难应付。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我现在最怕是没有人来供我们磨练。嘿！你在看甚么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你看不到扬起的尘头吗？说不定是追兵赶来呢。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 85,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    }
  ],
